      • nextStep

        boolean nextStep(double dt,
                 DynamicSimuMethod method)
        Calculate the controller's next step states x(t+1) = x(t) + dxdt * dt. All constraints, such as limits, should be applied. Return false if there is an error in the calculation
        Parameters:
        dt - the time step for solving the differential eqn.
